node.text: 2021 Giving Announcement! Hello Bello was founded on a promise - that we would commit to being right there with you, alongside our community, especially when life gets messy. To keep that going into 2021, @kristenanniebell ‘s here to announce Hello Bello Giving! Every week we’ll feature a new state in the U.S. (Canada will get love too!) to not only gift more families with a year’s worth of booty wrappers, but we’ll also be highlighting organizations doing good in their communities, so that we can give back together. Every week a new state. Every week more diapers. Stay tuned! #HelloBello
